  "notes": "2 LP | Opaque Gold [Limited Edition]\n\nReleased as a Barnes & Noble exclusive in the US. \n\nIncludes complete album notes and lyrics, also the lyrics to the songs that were omitted it earlier booklet(s): O Holy Night, Blue Christmas, Ave Maria, Adeste Fideles, The Christmas Song, Happy Xmas and Feliz Navidad.\n\nIn this release, the track \"I'm Your Angel\" is now replaced by \"I Met An Angel (On Christmas Day)\" as last song of the album, previously released on the That's The Way It Is single: [m134830].\n\n(P) 1998 Sony Music Entertainment Canada Inc. / Art de l'emballage (packing art) 1998, 2022 (C) Sony Music Entertainment Canada Inc.\nDistributed by Sony Music Entertainment\nMade in the EU ",
